Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter Playboy interview, September 1976
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjlj7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Sep 1976
Carter Playboy interview. Public reaction to Carter's 'adultery in my heart' admission. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less